included.description:
1. In this project we use hash message digest to create sign for the user with the help of RSA and verify the sign at the server side for the authentication of the user.
2. After the user is authenticated the user votes secretly with the help of RSA encryption and send its vote to the voting server where it is decrypted.
3. This project implements the secure socket programming and concurrent server also as multiple users can vote at same time.
included.title: SECURE VOTING SYSTEM

included.description:
1.	The goal of this project was to build parser for CSV file. After parsing the file we have to sort the
        file according to ssn number or last name.
2.	This project can sort csv records from multiple files and then merge the records from the sorted
        files to give the one merged sorted output.
3.	For merging I used different methods like pipes, shared memory and threads (Windows API)
